import {
    Navbar
} from "../../components"
import {
    useAuth
} from "../../hooks"
import "./address.css"
export const AddressPage = () => {
        const {
            authState: {
                user,
                token
            },
            authDispatch
        } = useAuth()
        return <div >
            <
            Navbar / >
            <
            div >
            <
            div className = "padding-lg address-fields" >
            <
            span className = "bd-dash padding-lg" > +ADD ADDRESS < /span> <
            /div> <
            form className = "flex-col width-fitContent address-fields" >
            <
            div >
            <
            h1 > userProfile < /h1> {
                token ? < h2 > {
                        user.firstName
                    } < /h2>:""} <
                    /div> <
                    div className = "user-box" >
                    <
                    label > Name < /label> <
                    input type = "text"
                placeholder = "first Name" /
                    >
                    <
                    /div>

                    <
                    input type = "text"
                placeholder = "Last Name" /
                    >
                    <
                    input type = "text"
                placeholder = "Phone Number" /
                    >
                    <
                    input type = "text"
                placeholder = "door number" / >
                    <
                    input type = "text"
                placeholder = "street" / >
                    <
                    input type = "text"
                placeholder = "pinCode" / >
                    <
                    button > Add < /button> <
                    button > Cancel < /button> <
                    /form> <
                    /div> <
                    /div>
            }
